          background color with a matching shadow for consistent elevation.
          Shadow classes (<code>shadow-1</code>, <code>shadow-2</code>, <code>shadow-3</code>) apply box-shadow only.
        </p>

        <div class="border border-radius padding">
          <div class="units-row">
